                        </g>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="compnay-name fs-4">Acme Widget Co</span>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="pricing-header p-3 pb-md-4 mx-auto text-center">
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-normal">Our offer</h1>
                <p class="main-text fs-5 text-muted">Enjoy unbeatable delivery savings with every purchase!
                For orders under $50, pay just <span class="price-regular">$4.95</span> for delivery.
                Orders between $50 and $90 enjoy a reduced delivery fee of <span class="price-reduced">$2.95</span>.
                Best of all, when you spend over $90, delivery is absolutely <span class="price-free">FREE!</span>
                Plus, we’re thrilled to offer an exclusive deal:
                Buy one red widget and get the second at <span class="offer-text">half price</span>.
                Don’t miss out on these amazing savings – <span class="offer-text">shop now</span> and make the most of our special offers!</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-normal text-center mb-5">Our Products</h1>
            <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 mb-3 text-center" id="products-list">
                {% for product in products %}
                    <div class="col">
                        <div class="card mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm">
                            <div class="card-header py-3">
                                <h4 class="my-0 fw-normal">{{product.product}}</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title">{{product.price}}$</small></h1>
                                <div class="form-check d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value={{product.code}} id="flexCheckChecked_{{product.code}}">
                                    <img class="basket-icon" src="public/assets/icons/basket.svg" alt="basket icon">
                                    <div data-mdb-input-init class="number-product w-25 form-outline">
                                        <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign trailing"></i>
                                        <input type="number" id="form1" class="form-control form-icon-trailing" value="0" min="0" step="any" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
    </main>
</body>
<footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
